**/.venv
.git
.github
**/dist
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/.vite
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.coverage
backend/schemas
docs
diagramme
*.log
Bildschirmfoto*.png
